replies.txt_content:
我把所有的Error/严重警告给您列出来
1.Error occurred while enabling SaneEconomy v0.13.1-SNAPSHOT (Is it up to date?)
SaneEconomy 此经济插件在载入存储数据库时出现错误，是不是您清错了？
如果您还有备份还好，没有备份只能重置数据（删掉配置重新生成）

2.[09:37:02] [Server thread/WARN]: [QuickShop] 无法找到经济管理类插件...
[09:37:02] [Server thread/WARN]: [QuickShop] 卸载插件!!!
这个是1造成，经济插件出了问题

3.[09:37:05] [Server thread/INFO]: [HeadDatabase] Enabling HeadDatabase v4.9.1
[09:37:05] [Server thread/INFO]: [HeadDatabase] Using default "en_US.lang" created by Arcaniax
[09:37:05] [Server thread/INFO]: [HeadDatabase] Economy plugin not found, some features will be disabled!
同2

4.[09:37:07] [Server thread/INFO]: [Residence] Scanning for economy systems...
[09:37:07] [Server thread/INFO]: [Residence] Found Vault, but Vault reported no usable economy system...
同2

5.[09:37:09] [Server thread/ERROR]: [GangsPlus] Plugin disabled due to no Vault/economy dependency found!
同

6.[CS-CoreLib] Task #55 for CS-CoreLib vv1.6 generated an exception
java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: com/sk89q/worldguard/WorldGuard
CS-CoreLib与WG版本似乎不兼容

7.[DeluxeMenus] Plugin DeluxeMenus v1.10.5 generated an exception while executing task 2714
java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: net/brcdev/gangs/GangsPlusApi
DeluxeMenus因为 5 没了所以挂了

您要解决的：大概只有1 ,6问题应该不严重。重置经济配置/或者换新的经济插件

有帮助请您在本回复右下角点击设置最佳答案。
您的认可是对回答者最大的支持！
